flowchart TD
    claim{NFS/mount sandbox\n검증 주장이 필요한가?}
    baseline[일반 CI / 로컬 기본 검증\ngo test ./...]
    privileged{privileged Linux +\nreachable disposable NFS exports?}
    skip[통합 skeleton은 t.Skip\nNFS 검증은 UNVERIFIED로 보고]
    inputs[FVS_TEST_* 입력 준비\nNFS host/export/subpath/verify roots]
    private[private disposable verify roots\nowner-only, no symlink components]
    skeleton[선택 실행\ngo test -tags='integration,nfs'\n-run TestNFSSyncSandboxE2E]
    runbook[수동 runbook 실행\nsudo env -i + select 0 one-row.csv]
    child[selector-launched sync child\nmount namespace sandbox]
    evidence[증거 수집\nstdout/stderr, findmnt, checksum, readlink, cleanup]
    report{증거가 모두 첨부됐는가?}
    verified[NFS 검증 완료 주장 가능\nrunbook/evidence 링크 필수]
    unverified[NFS/mount sandbox는\n미검증으로 보고]

    claim -- no --> baseline
    claim -- yes --> privileged
    privileged -- no --> skip --> unverified
    privileged -- yes --> inputs --> private
    private --> skeleton --> child
    private --> runbook --> child
    child --> evidence --> report
    report -- yes --> verified
    report -- no --> unverified
